HEADWORD: paysheet
<hw>pay"sheet`</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>the total amount of
money paid in wages; <as>as, the company had a large
<ex>paysheet</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> payroll.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>a list of employees and their salaries; <as>as, the
company had a long <ex>paysheet</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> payroll.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

